{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Prove your abilities to the stars and become the brightest constellation!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a world of countless tiers, stars are divided into zones based on the strength of their light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The protagonist, Pio, born with a faint light, begins their journey in the lowest tier, the Graveyard of Stars, yet carries a deep longing for the upper tiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To realize this dream, Pio takes on the <strong>Trials of the Stars</strong>, aiming to ascend to the higher realms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/\ubcc4\uc758\ubcc4_\uac8c\uc784_\uc2a4\ud06c\ub9b0\uc0f7_1.jpg?t=1737546550\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Overview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pio is a unique action platformer where players use the terrain they stand on to attack enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game's standout feature is that the player's bullets also serve as terrain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/\ubcc4\uc758\ubcc4_\uac8c\uc784_\uc2a4\ud06c\ub9b0\uc0f7_7.jpg?t=1737546550\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The more bullets you fire, the smaller the terrain becomes, demanding precise control. On the other hand, conserving bullets means enduring the onslaught of powerful monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience this innovative action gameplay as you strategically manage your terrain and bullets to overcome challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Dreamlike Constellation Worldview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you continue to face challenges, a more dreamlike world of stars unfolds.<br>Embark on a shining journey and explore a unique world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>'The Examination Hall of Stars'</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/\ubcc4\uc758\ubcc4_\uac8c\uc784_\uc2a4\ud06c\ub9b0\uc0f7_2.jpg?t=1737546550\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong> 'The Tomb of Stars'</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/\ubcc4\uc758\ubcc4_\uac8c\uc784_\uc2a4\ud06c\ub9b0\uc0f7_3.jpg?t=1737546550\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>'The City of Scattered Stars'</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/\ubcc4\uc758\ubcc4_\uac8c\uc784_\uc2a4\ud06c\ub9b0\uc0f7_8.jpg?t=1737546550\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>'Gort's Altar'</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/extras/\ubcc4\uc758\ubcc4_\uac8c\uc784_\uc2a4\ud06c\ub9b0\uc0f7_9.jpg?t=1737546550\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This project was created as part of the graduation work at\u00a0ChungKang College of Cultural Industries</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737546550","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737546550","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/0deb2449628375f9a52934de8d8bdd66740eabe6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737546550","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334400/0deb2449628375f9a52934de8d8bdd66740eabe6/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737546550","categories":[{"description":"Single